{"tid":1155324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"虛報與母同住　男子呃免稅額罪成","createTime":"2019-05-15T01:06:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-15T02:53:10.000Z","uid":6604,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2a2b56a467029fd03c683fee6e4cd0461ef14e8b","tid":1155324,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T01:06:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190515/20678673\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190515%2F20678673&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgV%2F%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=508bc987\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190515%2F20678673&h=5ae567c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190515/20678673</a><br />\n<br />\n打工仔近日陸續收到報稅表，謹記要如實填寫。一名42歲納稅人訛稱與母親在三個年度內全年同住，以騙取較供養非同住父母多一倍的免稅額，虛假申索供養父母額外免稅額合共11.4萬元，涉及稅款總額為13,607元，被裁定四項逃繳薪俸稅罪名成立。<br />\n三個年度少交1.3萬元<br />\n被告承認三項蓄意意圖逃稅，分別2011至2012年度、2012至2013年度及2014至2015年度，在報稅表訛稱其母親在上述課稅年度與他連續全年同住，涉及虛假申索供養父母額外免稅額合共11.4萬元，少交稅款達13,607元。<br />\n<br />\n稅務局展開調查，向該納稅人索取其母親住所資料，他給予虛假的書面答覆，聲稱其母親由2012年1月起與他在同一物業居住。稅務局調查後確認，兩人在該三個年度沒有連續一同居住。該納稅人亦承認涉及的一項蓄意意圖逃稅，昨被裁定四項逃繳薪俸稅罪名成立，法官將案件押後至下月4日判刑。<br />\n<br />\n稅務學會顧問委員會主席王銳強表示，供養同住父母的免稅額較非同住父母高出一倍，提醒稅務局雖不會查核所有報稅表，但會調查可疑個案，要求納稅人提供證明文件等，呼籲如實填報。<br />\n<br />\n稅務局表示，稅務條例一經定罪，每項控罪最高刑罰為入獄三年和罰款五萬元，另加一筆相等於少徵收稅款三倍的罰款。<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n之前有連登仔問點捉<br />\n原來咁快手就 prosecution case <br />\n$4,000 、公屋居屋綜援審查外判畀稅局做仲好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b2a787ad8904b620508222d0349a7e755436b51","tid":1155324,"uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T01:13:35.000Z","msg":"你估稅務局唔識用電腦search database咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12b12c55c0c189597d4b9716c14768aeb49b389e","tid":1155324,"uid":214087,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T01:21:04.000Z","msg":"點解吾揀其他選項填呀？？"},{"pid":"5411f75d116891d5f65acda33e4dd32377634991","tid":1155324,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T01:22:18.000Z","msg":"條友衰咩無啦啦畀稅局開file?<br />\n一街都係的士佬又唔查?"},{"pid":"12bd686d44a7e7704c12dcbfb792b8bb0d2efc27","tid":1155324,"uid":38757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b2a787ad8904b620508222d0349a7e755436b51","tid":1155324,"uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T01:13:35.000Z","msg":"你估稅務局唔識用電腦search database咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T01:23:20.000Z","msg":"其實好難check 到喎, 會唔會有人報寸?"},{"pid":"04bf0f566ad5de6601848051c579051e31d893d2","tid":1155324,"uid":48234,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"12b12c55c0c189597d4b9716c14768aeb49b389e","tid":1155324,"uid":214087,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T01:21:04.000Z","msg":"點解吾揀其他選項填呀？？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T01:24:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/2QYzReW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2QYzReW.gif&h=2dfbad24&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8d33b2ddee5428d71d99e39643d60edebcd5f7b","tid":1155324,"uid":65401,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T01:24:51.000Z","msg":"真係難check"},{"pid":"3a4800dbe4b95dbddfcba1b3afeaa62ed8a85ddf","tid":1155324,"uid":187544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T01:27:50.000Z","msg":"反而想知稅局點會開佢file，屎忽痕？無野搵野做？（